  "detailed_description": "Yasai Ninja is a Hack & Slash adventure set in a particular Feudal Japan  that tells the story of two veggie-heroes, Kaoru Tamanegi and Broccoli Joe, who will have to learn how to cooperate to fight their way through multiple dangers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFriendship, personal growth, honour and teamwork are combined in this epic tale.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnlock new abilities, levels and achievements, and use each character's special skills to beat puzzles and brawls in order to defeat the corrupt Shogun!",
  "about_the_game": "Yasai Ninja is a Hack & Slash adventure set in a particular Feudal Japan  that tells the story of two veggie-heroes, Kaoru Tamanegi and Broccoli Joe, who will have to learn how to cooperate to fight their way through multiple dangers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFriendship, personal growth, honour and teamwork are combined in this epic tale.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnlock new abilities, levels and achievements, and use each character's special skills to beat puzzles and brawls in order to defeat the corrupt Shogun!",
